.TH devin-cloud-drs-blueprint-create 1  "blueprint-create " 
.SH NAME
devin\-cloud\-drs\-blueprint\-create \- Create a new environment blueprint
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBdevin cloud drs blueprint\-create\fR [\fB\-\-repo\fR] [\fB\-\-from\-file\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Create a new environment blueprint
.PP
Creates a blueprint optionally scoped to a repository. Pass `\-\-from\-file` to seed it with an initial `environment.yaml`.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-repo\fR \fI<REPO>\fR
Repository to scope the blueprint to (e.g. `owner/repo`); omit for org\-wide
.TP
\fB\-\-from\-file\fR \fI<FROM_FILE>\fR
Path to a YAML file with the initial blueprint contents
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
